<i>noun</i>: 엉덩방아 [엉ː덩방아] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엉덩방아 [엉ː덩방아]</dt><br>
<dd>pratfall; fall on one's buttocks</dd><br>
<dd>미끄러지거나 넘어져 주저앉으면서 엉덩이를 바닥에 부딪치는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of allowing yourself to fall on the ground after pretending to slip or fall.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>